304775091.Title: Amana 21.4 cu. ft. Side by Side Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Silver
304775091.Description: Our 33 in. Amana Side-by-Side Refrigerator is great for smaller spaces, giving you the right amount of storage room. This 21 cu. ft. refrigerator with ice and water dispenser lets you grab fresh H2O with a Dual Pad Dispenser with EVERYDROP Water Filter. Easily set temps with Electronic Temperature Controls. And big items fit in the Gallon Door Storage Bins. Color: Stainless Steel.

302786603.Title: Whirlpool 21 cu. ft. Side by Side Refrigerator in Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel
302786603.Description: Get purposefully designed storage spaces for items you use most in this side-by-side refrigerator. An in-door can caddy frees up shelf space while frameless glass shelves in the refrigerator with ice and water dispenser lets you store more items on each shelf for loading flexibility. The deli drawer refrigerator gives you plenty of space to store meat and cheese, too. Color: Fingerprint Resistant Stainless Steel.

305502350.Title: Whirlpool 21 cu. ft. Side by Side Refrigerator in Black
305502350.Description: Fit and find it all with purposefully-designed storage spaces in this ENERGY STAR certified refrigerator. Get increased loading flexibility with adjustable gallon door bins. The refrigerator with ice and water dispenser lets you access ice and water without opening the door while LED lights keep food looking as good as it tastes. Color: Black.

302565681.Title: Frigidaire 22.1 cu. ft. Side by Side Refrigerator in Black
302565681.Description: The Frigidaire 22.1 cu. ft.
